The Natural Fantasy Atlas for Fabula Ultima will bring you into worlds deeply
permeated by the cycles of time and nature, where young heroes face the
consequences of past mistakes and demonstrate that history does not have to
repeat itself, creating a brave future of coexistence, much like in classic JRPGs!
