SPELLS
h Compact Terrain w 5 MP w Self w Scene.
Until this spell ends, the Back of Brightvale gains Resistance to physical damage. When the
Back goes into Crisis, this spell ends. The Back can’t cast this spell while in Crisis.
h Silent Call w 10 × T MP w Up to two creatures w Instantaneous.
Each target may perform a free attack with a weapon they have equipped (or a basic attack, if
