OTHER ACTIONS
S Sandy Dive w The Back of Brightvale can use an action and spend 20 Mind Points to dive
under the desert sand and suddenly reemerge. If it does, all enemies present on the scene
have to perform a Group Check【 INS + MIG】 with DL 10. If the Group Check fails, the Back
deals 15 earth damage to each enemy it can see, and those enemies also suffer shaken.
