Construct w The Back of Brightvale is immune to poisoned.
Sand and Dust w At the end of each of its turns, if the Back of Brightvale is in Crisis, it loses
10 Hit Points as its body slowly falls apart. If it reaches 0 Hit Points this way, all of its enemies
plummet to the ground, suffering 20 physical damage.
Without Conscience w The Back of Brightvale is immune to dazed, enraged and shaken.
